Name: Average time from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Median duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' compared to 'Completed + Resolved'
Average time between 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average lead time for 'Completed + Cancelled' from case start
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Longest time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Shortest time from 'Accepted + Wait - User' to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' compared to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Closed' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Total time of 'Completed + Cancelled' activities in the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Median time to 'Completed + Cancelled' grouped by 'org:group'
Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Longest and shortest duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' activities
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + Cancelled' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x00000221C2305210> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Average duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' compared to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Total time from first 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Cancelled' in a case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' in cases with more than one 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Variation in duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' over months
Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'
